title: Mythbusters Odds and Sods
description:
Included in this torrent is:

- DVD Covers for all Box Set and Specials.
- Episode Guide
- Missing full length Discovery Episodes.

So really this is an upload for the die hard fans.

I've got the missing episodes from other uploaders but I'm trying to get the full length episodes.

I have noticed that iTunes US has released some of them but I can't get them without a Geoblock remover, and I'm still messing around with this.

Anyhow, enjoy this info and more Bonus DVD's to come.

Ciao for now.
